fullText:
Read Mrs. Stantons
paper at the Emma
Juillard Congress - Mrs
Russell Sage Presiding -
attended reception at
Mrs McCormicks this P.M. -
summaryText: Susan B. Anthony read Mrs. Stanton's paper at the Emma Juillard Congress, attended a reception at Mrs. McCormick's in the afternoon, and Mrs. Russell Sage presided over the event.
